Widget I can click to get a print dialog.  Options:

- dimensions
    - x
    - y
    - default to edited areas, plus enough surrounding space to fill a
      rectangle
- border hexes dropdown: 
    - default tile background (e.g. grassland), or
    - black
- mode
    - map and notes [as HTML+SVG]
    - map and notes, numbered
    - PNG
    - PNG, numbered
    - SVG
    - SVG, numbered

